South Africa’s Malema Says Youth Wing to Subject Itself to ANC Discipline

-- B y   J a n a   M a r a i s
-- 
2011-08-29T12:04:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-29/south-africa-s-malema-says-youth-wing-to-subject-itself-to-anc-discipline.html
The leadership of the youth wing of
 South Africa ’s ruling  African National Congress  will subject
itself to party discipline, the Youth League’s President  Julius
Malema  said.  The league urged members to ensure that planned protests
during tomorrow’s ANC disciplinary hearings are peaceful, Malema
told reporters in Johannesburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Marais in Johannesburg at 
